data.description:
## Basic Settings
**Item:** ${tempVars('giveaway-item')}
**Winners:** ${tempVars('giveaway-count')}
**Duration:** ${tempVars('giveaway-durationFormatted')}
**Channel:** ${tempVars('giveaway-channelSelected')}

## Additional Settings
**Title:** ${tempVars('giveaway-title') || tempVars('giveaway-count')+"x "+tempVars('giveaway-item')}
**Description:** ${tempVars('giveaway-description') || tempVars('giveaway-count')+"x "+tempVars('giveaway-item')}
**Banner Link:** ${tempVars('giveaway-image') ? tempVars('giveaway-image') : "*NIL*"}
**Sponsors:** ${tempVars('giveaway-sponsors')?.length > 0 ? tempVars('giveaway-sponsorsFormatted') : "*NIL*"}
**Role Requirements:** ${tempVars('giveaway-roleRequirement')?.length > 0 ? tempVars('giveaway-roleRequirementFormatted') : "*NIL*"}

## Participants
${tempVars('giveaway-giveawayEntries').length == 0 ? "Nobody has joined this giveaway yet :sob:" : tempVars('giveaway-giveawayEntriesPages')[Number(tempVars('giveaway-viewParticipants-currentPage'))].join("\n")}

-# Viewing page ${Number(tempVars('giveaway-viewParticipants-currentPage')) + 1} of ${tempVars('giveaway-giveawayEntriesPages').length || 1}

${tempVars('giveaway-giveawayData').data.description}

**Hosted By:** <@${tempVars('giveaway-giveawayData').data.host}>${tempVars('giveaway-sponsors')?.length > 0 ? "\n**Sponsors:** " + tempVars('giveaway-sponsorsFormatted') : ""}
**Ended:** ${tempVars('giveaway-endTimeRelative')} (${tempVars('giveaway-endTimeFullDisp')})

**Winner${tempVars('giveaway-winners').length > 1 ? "s" : ""}:** ${tempVars('giveaway-winners').length > 0 ? tempVars('giveaway-winnersFormatted') : "Nobody won :sob:"}

-# Winner${tempVars('giveaway-winners').length > 1 ? "s" : ""} drawn on ${tempVars('giveaway-drawTimeFullDisp')}
